        <abstract> 
<p>Can only conjecture that the problem occurs because the plant is not living in its natural conditions. Refers to what he said on <hi rend="italic">Acropera</hi> [in <hi rend="italic">Orchids</hi>]. Many plants under culture have sexual functions altered.</p>  
<p>Asks PHG to look at bee <hi rend="italic">Ophrys</hi> at Torquay to see if pollinia are ever removed. "It is my greatest puzzle."</p> 
        </abstract>
